u_{\mu}} = 878.0 \pm 2.1 \pm 6.7 \pm 9.3 \pm 15.0 	ext{ pb} $$ and $$\sigma_{W^{-}ightarrow\mu^{-} ar{
u}_{\mu}} = 689.5 \pm 2.0 \pm 5.3 \pm 6.3 \pm 11.8 	ext{ pb}, $$ where the uncertainties are due to the sample size, systematic effects, the beam energy and the luminosity determination.
